3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses using machine learning techniques (specifically, reinforcement learning and neural networks) for solving integral equations.
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses using artificial intelligence techniques (specifically, reinforcement learning and neural networks) for solving integral equations.
5. cs.CG (Computational Geometry): The paper discusses using Monte Carlo and quasi-Monte Carlo methods for training neural networks, which are commonly used in computational geometry.
